  <meta name="keywords" content="XORZENX framework, sparse transformer architecture, FRAZIYM AI, HASS attention mechanism, sparse mixture of experts, latent chain of thought, efficient AI architecture, local AI model, Akik Faraji AI research, Bangladesh AI research, low compute AI, sparse adaptive intelligence"/>
